ancia de la emodina para combatir la diabetes, y aunque los cient\u00edficos aseguran que a\u00fan es muy pronto como para recomendarla oficialmente como un tratamiento contra esta enfermedad, es necesario continuar trabajando para que lo sea.", "language": null, "image": "https://st1.uvnimg.com/3a/60/ff8a1c114b0cb94b76cf39d1fdaa/newversion.jpg", "pagetype": "website", "links": ["https://www.univision.com/carros", "https://www.univision.com/delicioso", "https://www.tudn.com", "https://www.tudn.com/futbol", "https://www.tudn.com/futbol/liga-mx", "https://www.tudn.com/futbol/uefa-champions-league", "https://www.tudn.com/boxeo", "https://www.tudn.com/futbol/resultados-y-estadisticas-futbol", "https://www.univision.com/estilo-de-vida", "https://www.univision.com/famosos", "https://www.univision.com/horoscopos", "https://www.univision.com/local", "https://www.univision.com/noticias", "https://www.univision.com/noticias/america-latina", "https://www.univision.com/coronavirus", "https://www.univision.com/noticias/estados-unidos", "https://www.univision.com/univision-news", "https://www.univision.com/noticias/politica", "https://www.univision.com/noticias/inmigracion", "https://www.univision.com/noticias/mundo", "https://www.univision.com/radio", "https://www.univision.com", "https://shop.univision.com/?utm_source=Univision&utm_medium=widget&utm_campaign=Home", "https://tv.univision.com/channels?seoName=univision&utm_source=univisioncom&utm_medium=nav-watchbutton&utm_campaign=TVE-2019-seoName", "https://vix.smart.link/nf1l32vsc?site_id=univision&creative_id=evergreen&lpurl=https://vix.com/es/canales&cp_1=internal_referral&cp_2=0&cp_3=top_nav&cp_4=0", "https://www.univision.com/local", "https://www.univision.com/shows", "https://www.univision.com/noticias", "https://www.univision.com/famosos", "https://www.tudn.com", "https://www.univision.com/estilo-de-vida", "https://www.univision.com/radio", "https://shop.univision.com/", "https://www.univision.com/estilo-de-vida", "https